data.description: Freshly remodeled and updated, this beautiful home sits on over an acre homesite, surrounded by woods and more expensive homes in unique, quiet enclave. Light-filled kitchen features new cabinets, new stainless appliances including refrigerator, quartz countertops with tile backsplash, island with seating area, hardwood floors throughout up- and downstairs. Wraparound covered front porch provides peaceful spot to sit and drink coffee or tea, and deck and large gazebo are perfect for outdoor entertaining in spacious back yard. Rare opportunity for country living with city convenience as situated just over Union County line (low taxes yet close to shopping and restaurants). Oversized three-car garage features 8-foot header height with extra paver parking spot behind garage. Lots of offstreet parking. Short walk to the Olde Sycamore Golf Plantation clubhouse/grill.
